        "file_id": 148,
        "finding_type": "theological_note",
        "finding": "The Hebrews new covenant quotation (Heb 8:10; 10:16) names both dianoia (mind) and kardia (heart) as sites of internalized law — anticipating the structural relationship between Registries 112 and 183 for Session D investigation.",
        "anchor_verses": "Heb 8:10, Heb 10:16",
